Now you'll need to choose the <color class="yellow">race</color> of your character. Here are your options:
  1) <color class="blue">Human:</color> Adaptable and diverse in skills.
  2) <color class="blue">Elf:</color> Graceful and attuned to nature.
  3) <color class="blue">Dwarf:</color> Resilient craftsmen with strong endurance.
  4) <color class="blue">Dragonborn:</color> Wise beings with draconic blood.
  5) <color class="blue">Centaur:</color> Majestic warriors with swiftness.
  6) <color class="blue">Orc:</color> Fierce warriors known for their strength.